<br/>
the collection is a poetrip from girlhood into womanhood, as fathers reveal glass sparrows hidden between their ribs, and women converse with their mute skeletons, capturing bits of love both playful, and hideous.<br/>
<br/>
it will be available for browsing/buying at SUPeR starting 12:00 on Saturday<br/>
<br/>
fuss fee tickets and more info at supertimebooks.com/events<br/>
<br/>
